snippet.textDisplay: Onek kichu bujhi nah Aaj kal jemon gaan ... temni bujhi nah keno Zimbabwe amader (bangladesh) catch miss korle Bangladeshi audience vua vua bole…. So Aaj kal shob kichu bujhar bahire chole jacche!!! 3rd season taa onek taa matha r upore diye jacche. Bujhlam nah gaan gulo ki amader entertainment er jonoo naki kono ekta special competition or to impress specific!!! Anyways 2:30secs theke rap taa seii lagse mone hoy oiii koto tuku bujhecchi. Valo lagto bujhtam shuntam akhon bujhi nah hoyto aar shunbona. But amader onek experiments jate abar ulto nah hoye jay. Areeh baba ami against e nah just bollam Best of luck!!!!
